---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="NaMiSmart is owned and operated by Vick Sarkis — 10+ years of security camera and enterprise networking experience across Greater LA.">

<style>
  .sec{position:relative;z-index:4;padding:30px 56px 20px;}
  .eyebrow{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.24em;color:#4DA6FF;margin-bottom:14px;}
  .crumb{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:#5E6C86;margin-bottom:18px;}
  .crumb a{color:#5E6C86;}
  .hero-panel{border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:20px;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0D1220,#0A0E17);padding:46px 48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;gap:44px;align-items:center;}
  .hero-panel h1{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:50px;line-height:0.98;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:#fff;max-width:560px;margin:0;}
  .hero-panel p{font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:#98A4BA;margin:22px 0 0;max-width:520px;}
  .hero-panel p.sm{font-size:15px;color:#8B98AE;margin:14px 0 0;}
  .owner-sig{margin-top:26px;padding-top:22px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);}
  .owner-sig .name{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:20px;color:#fff;}
  .owner-sig .title{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#4DA6FF;margin-top:5px;}
  .portrait-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;}
  .portrait{position:relative;width:100%;aspect-ratio:0.66;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);background:radial-gradient(120% 90% at 50% 8%,#14243E 0%,#0D1526 42%,#080C15 100%);}
  .portrait-grid{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(90,140,220,0.06) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(90,140,220,0.06) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;pointer-events:none;}
  .portrait-glow{position:absolute;left:50%;top:16%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:70%;height:70%;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(77,166,255,0.20),transparent 68%);filter:blur(24px);pointer-events:none;}
  .portrait img{position:absolute;left:50%;bottom:0;transform:translateX(-50%);height:96%;width:auto;object-fit:contain;filter:drop-shadow(0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.55));}
  .portrait-caption{position:absolute;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;padding:22px 22px 16px;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(6,9,15,0.92),rgba(6,9,15,0));z-index:2;}
  .portrait-caption .n{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:18px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-0.01em;}
  .portrait-caption .t{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#9AA6BC;margin-top:4px;}
  .creds-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;}
  .cred{border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:16px;background:#0E131D;padding:22px 24px;}
  .cred .num{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:30px;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;}
  .cred .lbl{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#7C89A0;margin-top:6px;}
  .how-panel{border:1px solid rgba(77,166,255,0.25);border-radius:20px;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0C1626,#0A1220);padding:44px 48px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .how-glow{position:absolute;top:-90px;right:-40px;width:320px;height:320px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(77,166,255,0.18),transparent 65%);filter:blur(30px);pointer-events:none;}
  .how-panel h2{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:32px;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#fff;margin:0 0 26px;max-width:640px;}
  .how-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:22px;}
  .how-item .t{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:17px;color:#fff;}
  .how-item p{font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;color:#8B98AE;margin:8px 0 0;}
  @media(max-width:860px){
    .sec{padding:20px 16px;}
    .hero-panel{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:28px;padding:28px 20px;}
    .hero-panel h1{font-size:40px;}
    .creds-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
    .how-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  }
</style>

<section class="sec">
  <div class="crumb"><a href="/">HOME</a> / <span style="color:#9AA6BC">ABOUT</span></div>
  <div class="hero-panel">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">// MEET THE OWNER</div>
      <h1>Hi, I'm Vick — and I install every system like it's my own.</h1>
      <p>I started NaMiSmart because I was tired of seeing rushed, cookie-cutter camera jobs. I combine real camera expertise with genuine networking knowledge — because a great camera system depends on the network behind it.</p>
      <p class="sm">With over a decade of hands-on work across residential, commercial, and enterprise projects, I'm on-site for the details that matter: clean installs, reliable systems, and the kind of support that's still there years later.</p>
      <div class="owner-sig">
        <div class="name">Vick Sarkis</div>
        <div class="title">OWNER · FOUNDER · LEAD TECHNICIAN</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="portrait-wrap">
      <div class="portrait">
        <div class="portrait-grid"></div>
        <div class="portrait-glow"></div>
        <img src="/images/owner-portrait.png" alt="Vick Sarkis, owner and lead technician of NaMiSmart" />
        <div class="portrait-caption">
          <div class="n">Vick Sarkis</div>
          <div class="t">OWNER · LEAD TECHNICIAN</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec" style="padding-top:8px;padding-bottom:12px">
  <div class="eyebrow">// EXPERIENCE & CREDENTIALS</div>
  <div class="creds-grid">
    <div class="cred"><div class="num">10+</div><div class="lbl">YEARS IN BUSINESS</div></div>
    <div class="cred"><div class="num">CCNA</div><div class="lbl">NETWORKING KNOWLEDGE</div></div>
    <div class="cred"><div class="num" style="font-size:20px">Digital Watchdog</div><div class="lbl">IPVMS CERTIFIED</div></div>
    <div class="cred"><div class="num" style="font-size:20px">CCIE partner</div><div class="lbl">ADVANCED ENTERPRISE</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec" style="padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:10px">
  <div class="how-panel">
    <div class="how-glow"></div>
    <div style="position:relative">
      <div class="eyebrow">// HOW WE WORK</div>
      <h2>Clean work, reliable systems, and support that lasts.</h2>
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div class="how-item"><div class="t">We design the full system</div><p>Cameras, cabling, network, storage, and remote access — planned together, not bolted on.</p></div>
        <div class="how-item"><div class="t">We install it cleanly</div><p>Neat cabling, labeled racks, and tidy placement you'll be glad to show off.</p></div>
        <div class="how-item"><div class="t">We stick around</div><p>Ongoing support, upgrades, and expansion as your property and needs grow.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div>
    <div class="eyebrow" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)">// WORK WITH NaMiSmart</div>
    <h2>Let's design yours.</h2>
    <p>Camera &amp; network systems across Greater LA.</p>
  </div>
  <a href="/contact" class="btn-dark">Get a quote</a>
</section>

</Layout>
